  <summary date="2015-07-28T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Government Refusal of Abortion in Contracting and Enterprise or the GRACE Act

This bill prohibits a federal entity from entering into a contract with a person or entity that donates or matches employee donations to Planned Parenthood Federation of America, Inc.,&#160;or any of its affiliates or clinics. This prohibition applies to contracts entered into after the enactment of this Act and to subcontracts (at any tier) awarded under such contracts.</summary>
